      <title>美国军方称伊斯兰国在索马里的势力增加了一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/islamic-state-doubles-its-presence-in-somalia-us-military-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国非洲司令部司令称，全球恐怖组织索马里伊斯兰国在非洲之角国家的分支机构今年在索马里的军事存在增加了一倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/islamic-state-doubles-its-presence-in-somalia-us-military-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:32:43 GMT</pubDate>
